data.description: Stunning Top Level Condo with Vaulted Ceilings, Designer Touches and Detached 2 Car Garage.  Easy Floorplan with Sprawling Family Room with Access to Private Balcony.  Eat In Kitchen with Closet Pantry.   Tranquil Master Bedroom with Custom Wainscotting, Attached En Suite Bathroom and Walk In Closet.  2 Additional Bedrooms, 2nd Full Bathroom and Dedicated Laundry Room.  Fantastic Saratoga Springs Location , Walking Distance to Schools, Parks and Access to Miles of Walking & Biking Paths.  Easy Access to Main Roads for Commuting.   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
